HEADWORD: Orchidales
<hw>Orchidales</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>An order of plants with
irregular flowers having minute seeds, and including the families
<fam>Orchidaceae</fam> and <fam>Burmanniaceae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Orchidales</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
